<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ʿạysẖyn mʿạk fy hnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ʿạysẖyn mʿạk fy hnạ
 wfy nṣrẗ wlw f ḍyqạt
 trạnym ạ̉frạḥ wgẖnạ
 wṣlạẗ fy kl ạlạ̉wqạt
 1- njynạ mn ạlsẖryr .. mn ḍgẖṭ wkẖwf wqywd
 ḥrrnạ mn tạ̉tẖyr .. ʿạlm mạdy wmḥdwd
 2- njynạ mn ḍʿfạtnạ .. m ạlsẖk wm ạlạ̉kạdẖyb
 ạẓhr ḥqk fy ḥyạtnạ .. wtẖmạr ʿml ạlṣlyb
 3- njynạ mn nfsynạ .. mn jhl wḍʿf ạ̹ymạn
 nwr fynạ wḥwạlynạ .. bsẖhạdẗ f kl mkạn</lyrics>
<author>wsym ʿạdl, rạndw hạrfy</author>
<hymn_number>11091</hymn_number>
</song>